---
// Problem/Solution Section
---

<section class="relative py-20 md:py-28">
  <!-- Decorative vertical line -->
  <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-[var(--border)] to-transparent hidden md:block">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] shadow-[0_0_12px_var(--accent-glow-strong)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-3/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--text-faded)]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-16">
      <!-- Problem -->
      <div class="relative">
        <p class="section-label">
          The Problem
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-3xl">
          AI isn't really personalized to you
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Every AI tool treats you like a stranger. It doesn't know your projects,
          your preferences, or how you work. You're constantly re-explaining context,
          spawning generic agents that don't fit your needs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Solution -->
      <div class="relative">
        <p class="section-label">
          The Solution
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-3xl">
          An AI system built around <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">you</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          OpenAgent is a configuration layer for OpenCode that makes AI truly personal.
          Persistent memory, specialized agents tailored to your workflow,
          and a system that evolves with your needs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
